Hewlett-Packard Co's Enterprise Services Italia S.r.l. To Supply Luxottica With Data Center Services
Thursday, 10 Jan 2013 07:45am EST
Hewlett-Packard Co's Enterprise Services Italia S.r.l. announced that Luxottica Group S.p.A., is in the design, manufacture and distribution of fashion, luxury and sports eyewear, has signed an agreement for Hewlett-Packard Co to manage its data center environment. Under the agreement, HP and Luxottica will work to create a more agile, secure and scalable technology infrastructure that helps Luxottica migrate to a cloud computing environment. The Company's journey to a cloud computing environment is focused on standardization to reduce risk and improve governance of IT operations.Â 
